    <item>
      <title>美国政府正在驱动1.8万亿美元的ESG市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/a-1-8-trillion-esg-market-is-being-driven-by-the-us-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可持续债务市场的1.8万亿美元的角落正在违背更广泛的经济下滑，因为投资者抢购了美国政府机构在很大程度上出售的债券，即使唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导了绿色撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/a-1-8-trillion-esg-market-is-being-driven-by-the-us-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当贸易商潜入技术：市场包裹时，美国期货集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/asian-stocks-under-pressure-as-uncertainty-rises-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股票期货集会，纳斯达克100指数的合同飙升了1.4％，因为交易者抢购了被打败的科技股，并从美国关税可能更有针对性的迹象的迹象中获得了乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/asian-stocks-under-pressure-as-uncertainty-rises-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 22:28:10 GMT</pubDate>
